invalid type: string "Object Detection with YOLO\nWhat is Object Detection?\nObject detection finds and classifies multiple objects in an image. It outputs bounding boxes\n(x, y, width, height) and class labels with confidence scores.\nYOLO ‚Äî You Only Look Once\n\u{7f} Single neural network processes entire image at once\n\u{7f} Divides image into S x S grid cells\n\u{7f}ce statistics\n\u{7f}ˇˇˇ